             were indicted for <rs id="t18340220-135-off791" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18340220-135-off791" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340220-135-off791" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18340220-135-cd792" type="crimeDate">18th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340220-135-off791 t18340220-135-cd792"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18340220-135-victim1362" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Davis
                        <interp inst="t18340220-135-victim1362" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
